==French==

===Relative pronoun===
'''lequel''' ''m'', '''[[lesquels]]''' ''pl'', '''[[laquelle]]''' ''f'', '''[[lesquelles]]''' ''fpl''
# which, that, whom
#:''Elle prefere l'homme, avec '''lequel''' tu sortais.''
#::''She prefers the man, with whom you you were going out/who you were going out with.''
'''lequel?'''
# (''in an interrogative sense) [[which]] one?
#:''Passe-moi le ballon.'' - '''''Lequel? Il y'en a trois.''
#:''Pass me the ball.'' - ''Which one? There are three.''

